# =============================================================================
# REGISTERED USERS — role verification for all 5 test accounts
# Base URL: https://todu.mn/bs/lms/v1
# Requires: VS Code REST Client extension
#
# Role IDs returned by the API (GET /roles):
#   0  → Хэрэглэгч  (user)
#   10 → Админ      (admin)
#   20 → Сургагч    (teacher)
#   30 → Суралцагч  (student)
#


# Account	role.id	App key	Guard
# admin@must.edu.mn	10	"admin"	isAdmin = true
# User@must.edu.mn	0	"user"	—
# schooladmin@must.edu.mn	10	"admin"	isAdmin = true
# schoolteacher@must.edu.mn	20	"teacher"	isTeacher = true
# schoolstudent@must.edu.mn	30	"student"	isStudent = true

# =============================================================================

@baseUrl = https://todu.mn/bs/lms/v1
@token   = iP-47AecuxD-Th3xdbLpxw

# =============================================================================
# 0. REFERENCE — all available roles
# =============================================================================

### GET /roles — full roles list (run with any valid token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# =============================================================================
# 1. СИСТЕМИЙН АДМИН — admin@must.edu.mn  (role id 10 → "admin")
# =============================================================================

### [1a] Login as system admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/token/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@must.edu.mn",
  "password": "123",
  "push_token": ""
}

###

### [1b] Get admin profile  → check id, email, schools[].role
# Paste token from [1a] into @token first
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### [1c] Get admin's schools with per-school role
# Replace 535 with the id returned in [1b]
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/535/schools
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# =============================================================================
# 2. СИСТЕМИЙН ХЭРЭГЛЭГЧ — User@must.edu.mn  (role id 0 → "user")
# =============================================================================

### [2a] Login as system user
POST {{baseUrl}}/token/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "User@must.edu.mn",
  "password": "123",
  "push_token": ""
}

###

### [2b] Get user profile  → check schools[].role
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# =============================================================================
# 3. СУРГУУЛИЙН АДМИН — schooladmin@must.edu.mn  (role id 10 → "admin")
# =============================================================================

### [3a] Login as school admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/token/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "schooladmin@must.edu.mn",
  "password": "123",
  "push_token": ""
}

###

### [3b] Get school-admin profile  → schools[].role.id should be 10
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# =============================================================================
# 4. СУРГУУЛИЙН БАГШ — schoolteacher@must.edu.mn  (role id 20 → "teacher")
# =============================================================================

### [4a] Login as teacher
POST {{baseUrl}}/token/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "schoolteacher@must.edu.mn",
  "password": "123",
  "push_token": ""
}

###

### [4b] Get teacher profile  → schools[].role.id should be 20
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# =============================================================================
# 5. СУРГУУЛИЙН ОЮУТАН — schoolstudent@must.edu.mn  (role id 30 → "student")
# =============================================================================

### [5a] Login as student
POST {{baseUrl}}/token/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "schoolstudent@must.edu.mn",
  "password": "123",
  "push_token": ""
}

###

### [5b] Get student profile  → schools[].role.id should be 30
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

